Multi-Client Test: Result: Passed. Confirmed the design successfully services requests from multiple different source ports.

Throughput/Bandwidth Test: Result: 94.97 Mbps. Achieved near-maximum wire-speed performance on the 100 Mbps RMII physical layer.

